title: ISic002946. Dedication to Artemis
body:
Facsimile Images

Επὶ Δινυσίου ἱ[ερέως]
Φιλοκράτης καὶ Ξ[ένων?]
Ἀρτέμιτι εὐ[χην]

Apparatus criticus

Text of Manganaro 1965

translation

In the priesthood of Dionysios. Philokrates and Xenon(?), (made) a vow to Artemis

commentary

Classified as a fake by Kaibel, without autopsy, both Orsi and Manganaro's autopsy confirms the text as genuine
